casebody.data:
Joseph H. Keller, et al., respondents, v. Edwin J. Denning, Jr., appellant. Decided February 4, 1884. Appeal from order directing defendant to accept service of complaint, Martin & Smith, for appellant; Sul*527livan & Cromwell, for respondent.

Before Sedgwick, Ch. J., Truax and O’ Gorman, J J.

Opinion Per Curiam. Order affirmed, with costs.
